# Skill Location Policy

- Create new skills only under `skills/<skill-name>/` in this repository.
- Do not create project skills under global user paths such as `~/.cursor/skills/`.
- When migrating an external skill into this project, place it in `skills/` and update docs (`README.md`, `docs/skills_catalog.md`) plus license/attribution notes if needed.
